## 🔌 Access Methods

### SSH Access
```bash
ssh -p 2222 devuser@localhost
# Password: turboflow
```

### VNC Desktop
```bash
# VNC Client connection
vnc://localhost:5901
# Password: turboflow

# Or use any VNC client:
# Server: localhost:5901
# Password: turboflow
```

### Management API
```bash
# Health check
curl http://localhost:9090/health

# API documentation (Swagger UI)
http://localhost:9090/documentation

# Requires X-API-Key header for authenticated endpoints
```

### Z.AI Service (Internal)
```bash
# From within container or ragflow network
curl http://localhost:9600/health

# Used by Claude skills for cost-effective API calls
```

