## 🔧 Build Fixes Applied

1. ✅ **DBus PID cleanup** - Stale PID files removed
2. ✅ **VNC GL extension** - Disabled GLX to prevent segfault
3. ✅ **XFCE4 dbus configuration** - Proper DBUS_SESSION_BUS_ADDRESS
4. ✅ **XDG_RUNTIME_DIR** - Created /run/user/1000 for devuser
5. ✅ **Software rendering** - LIBGL_ALWAYS_SOFTWARE=1 for stability
6. ✅ **Supervisord log directory** - /var/log/supervisor created
7. ✅ **code-server optional** - Made optional due to argon2 build failure

