## 🚀 Next Steps

### Immediate Use
```bash
# Connect via SSH
ssh -p 2222 devuser@localhost

# Or connect via VNC
# VNC Server: localhost:5901
# Password: turboflow

# Start Claude Code session
claude

# Use Claude Flow
npx claude-flow@alpha init --verify --pair
```

### Container Management
```bash
# View logs
docker logs -f turbo-flow-unified

# Restart services
docker exec turbo-flow-unified /opt/venv/bin/supervisorctl restart all

# Stop container
docker stop turbo-flow-unified

# Start container
docker start turbo-flow-unified

# Remove container
docker stop turbo-flow-unified && docker rm turbo-flow-unified
```

